<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>战区</title><link>https://www.twz.com</link><description>防御世界的强大进攻。</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 09 Jun 2026 03:29:50 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>VC-25B 空军一号“桥梁”飞机现在涂上了特朗普喜欢的红、白、蓝油漆</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/vc-25b-air-force-one-bridge-aircraft-now-wears-trumps-preferred-red-white-and-blue-paint-job</link><description>&lt;p&gt;VC-25B“桥”喷气式飞机也在今年夏天正式首次亮相之前进行最后一轮改装。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/vc-25b-air-force-one-bridge-aircraft-now-wears-trumps-preferred-red-white-and-blue-paint-job"&gt;VC-25B 后的空军一号“桥梁”飞机现在涂上了特朗普喜欢的红、白、蓝油漆，&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jun 2026 01:09:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/vc-25b-air-force-one-bridge-aircraft-now-wears-trumps-preferred-red-white-and-blue-paint-job</guid></item><item><title>硫磺岛号完成部署，尼米兹返回美国</title><link>https://www.twz.com/sea/iwo-jima-completes-deployment-nimitz-heading-back-to-the-united-states</link><description>&lt;p&gt;以下是截至 2026 年 6 月 8 日美国航空母舰和大型两栖攻击舰的位置。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/sea/iwo-jima-completes-deployment-nimitz-heading-back-to-the-united-states"&gt;硫磺岛完成部署后，尼米兹返回美国&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jun 2026 21:21:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/sea/iwo-jima-completes-deployment-nimitz-heading-back-to-the-united-states</guid></item><item><title>法德未来战斗机努力因不可调和的分歧而失败</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/franco-german-future-fighter-effort-collapses-over-irreconcilable-differences</link><description>&lt;p&gt;德国和法国未能就要求达成一致，这显然导致了欧洲旗舰下一代战斗机计划的结束。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;后&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/franco-german-future-fighter-effort-collapses-over-irreconcilable-differences"&gt;法德未来战斗机努力因不可调和的分歧而崩溃&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jun 2026 20:44:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/franco-german-future-fighter-effort-collapses-over-irreconcilable-differences</guid></item><item><title>KC-135 加油机被发现配备新型卫星通信天线</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/kc-135-tanker-sporting-new-large-antenna-points-to-major-communications-upgrade</link><description>&lt;p&gt;美国空军表示，改善连接性对于 KC-135 机队的生存能力和有效性至关重要。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/kc-135-tanker-sporting-new-large-antenna-points-to-major-communications-upgrade"&gt;配备新卫星通信天线的 KC-135 加油机&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jun 2026 19:40:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/kc-135-tanker-sporting-new-large-antenna-points-to-major-communications-upgrade</guid></item><item><title>伊朗和以色列从悬崖边退了一步</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/iran-and-israel-step-back-from-the-brink</link><description>&lt;p&gt;经过一系列针锋相对的打击后，以色列和伊朗退出了另一场全面战争。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/iran-and-israel-step-back-from-the-brink"&gt;伊朗和以色列从悬崖边退后&lt;/a&gt;一文首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jun 2026 18:06:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/iran-and-israel-step-back-from-the-brink</guid></item><item><title>空客推出 U145 无人货运直升机</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/airbus-unveils-u145-uncrewed-cargo-helicopter</link><description>&lt;p&gt;U145 将欧洲最成功的直升机之一转变为专为危险货运任务而优化的无人驾驶飞机。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/airbus-unveils-u145-uncrewed-cargo-helicopter"&gt;空中客车公司推出 U145 无人货运直升机&lt;/a&gt;后，首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jun 2026 17:50:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/airbus-unveils-u145-uncrewed-cargo-helicopter</guid></item><item><title>视频捕捉到阵风战斗机在波罗的海上空的无人机击落</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/video-captures-rafale-fighters-drone-kill-over-baltic</link><description>&lt;p&gt;这似乎是欧洲此类交战的首个镜头，凸显了无人机对北约空中警务构成的日益严峻的挑战。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/video-captures-rafale-fighters-drone-kill-over-baltic"&gt;视频捕捉到阵风战斗机在波罗的海上空无人机击落的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;“战区”&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jun 2026 15:59:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/video-captures-rafale-fighters-drone-kill-over-baltic</guid></item><item><title>伊朗对以色列发动弹道导弹袭击（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/iran-launches-ballistic-missile-attacks-on-israel</link><description>&lt;p&gt;在德黑兰周日针对以色列国防军轰炸贝鲁特而发动袭击后，伊朗和以色列之间再次发生公开冲突的可能性上升。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/iran-launches-ballistic-missile-attacks-on-israel"&gt;伊朗对以色列发射弹道导弹攻击（更新）&lt;/a&gt;一文首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jun 2026 03:01:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/iran-launches-ballistic-missile-attacks-on-israel</guid></item><item><title>F-47 的奇异形状隐藏在单位补丁上的显眼位置</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/f-47s-exotic-shape-was-hiding-in-plain-sight-on-a-unit-patch</link><description>&lt;p&gt;波音公司的 NGAD 演示机独特的平面形状在一块补丁上得到了暗示，就像它的前身猛禽一样。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;后&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/f-47s-exotic-shape-was-hiding-in-plain-sight-on-a-unit-patch"&gt;F-47 的奇异形状隐藏在单位补丁上的明显视野中，&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;中。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jun 2026 20:44:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/f-47s-exotic-shape-was-hiding-in-plain-sight-on-a-unit-patch</guid></item><item><title>与疣猪武器教练一起参观 A-10 驾驶舱和漫步之旅</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/a-10-cockpit-and-walk-around-tour-with-a-warthog-weapons-instructor</link><description>&lt;p&gt;我们在内利斯空军基地的航线上与疣猪进行了近距离接触。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;后&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/a-10-cockpit-and-walk-around-tour-with-a-warthog-weapons-instructor"&gt;A-10 驾驶舱和疣猪武器教练的漫步之旅&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jun 2026 16:59:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/a-10-cockpit-and-walk-around-tour-with-a-warthog-weapons-instructor</guid></item></channel></rss>